extends Object
implements Fn3<BiFunction<? super A,? super B,? extends C>,AppA,AppB,AppC>
    Lift into and apply a BiFunction to two Applicative values, returning the result inside the same Applicative context. Functionally equivalent to appB.zip(appA.fmap(fn)).
    See Also:
    Applicative.zip(Applicative)
